<epubChapter>
<epubPage>
<richtexts>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>提出了“白板说”，肯定儿童教育的可能性和价 值。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>提出了旗帜鲜明的“自然教育”理论，深深影响了后世教育理论的发展。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>倡导并实施爱的教育；</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_begin_tool1">
<text_indent>0</text_indent>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>主张教育心理化，强调教育要适应儿童身心自然发展要求；</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_begin_tool1">
<text_indent>0</text_indent>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>提出并阐述了要素主义教育理论；</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_begin_tool1">
<text_indent>0</text_indent>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>主张儿童应该尽早教育。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>撰写了世界上第一本学前教育专著《母育学校》，为儿童编写了《世界图解》作为教材；</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_begin_tool1">
<text_indent>0</text_indent>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>提出每个家庭都是一所母育学校，母亲就是老师，教育内容包括体育、智育和德育，详细论述了各方面教育的内容和方法；</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_begin_tool1">
<text_indent>0</text_indent>
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>充分肯定儿童的价值，把0－6周岁儿童的教育纳入其充满民主色彩的学制系统的第一阶段。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>主张儿童共有，教育公有，最早论述儿童优生问题。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>主张教育要与人的自然发展相适应。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
<richText type="complextext"><rich_text_item type="text_type_prefix_dot_tool1">
</rich_text_item>
<rich_text_item type="text_type_text_tool1">
<font_color>#444444</font_color>
<font_size>20</font_size>
<font_family>Palatino</font_family>
<text>主张对儿童的教育应是鼓励的，能激发他们兴趣的。</text>
<is_italic>false</is_italic>
<is_bold>false</is_bold>
</rich_text_item>
</richText>
